## PRODUCT OBJECTIVES

Product-specific objectives that support company objectives and drive product development.

### Objective 1 - Deliver AI-Powered Insights
**Description:** Integrate AI capabilities throughout the product to automate analysis and surface actionable insights.

**Key Results:**
- Launch AI-powered insights dashboard with 80% accuracy rate
- Achieve 60% daily active usage of AI features among paid users
- Reduce time spent on manual data analysis by 70% as reported by users

### Objective 2 - Enhance Platform Integration Capabilities
**Description:** Expand integrations with third-party tools to create a unified data ecosystem.

**Key Results:**
- Launch 10 new integrations with top requested tools
- Achieve 90% data sync reliability across all integrations
- Enable bi-directional sync for top 5 integrations

### Objective 3 - Improve Platform Performance and Reliability
**Description:** Ensure the platform can scale with customer growth while maintaining excellent performance.

**Key Results:**
- Achieve 99.9% uptime SLA
- Reduce page load times to under 2 seconds for 95th percentile
- Support 10x increase in data volume without performance degradation

